{"tid":1006353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25國70%人指中國變重要","createTime":"2019-02-03T02:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T03:37:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e94f9e23b0078281665dd412968bfc551af86e39","tid":1006353,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190203/20605517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F20605517&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=77e7661b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F20605517&h=f20e8e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190203/20605517</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月03日 <br />\n<br />\n25國70%人指中國變重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190203/large/a1105a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190203%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.gif&h=3aaa12f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國皮尤研究中心整合去年各項民調結果，發現幾個趨勢：年輕人比長者較傾向遠離facebook ；美國合法或非法入境的移民人數創新低；大多數人認為中國（圖）變重要，但傾向世界由美國領導；70%人關注校園槍擊案和氣候變化。<br />\n<br />\n中美角力方面，25國受訪者中，70%認為中國比10年前更重要，但63%人認為還是由美國領導世界較好；39%人認為經濟強國是美國，34%認為是中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青少年傾向遠離fb<br />\n<br />\n在網絡應用方面，59%青少年曾遇網絡欺凌，90%人認為有問題。越來越多年輕人刪除facebook手機應用程式，18歲以下的有26%、18至29歲有44%、65歲以上的僅12%。但網絡力量亦鼓勵Twitter上「#MeToo」運動興起，至去年9月底，該標籤在被使用超過1,900萬次。雖然調查發現Twitter賬號中約66%出自機械人，約34%出自人類。#MeToo亦蔓延至教會，但認同教宗方濟各處理手法的教徒從2015年的55%跌至31%。<br />\n<br />\n移民問題亦困擾美國，其接收難民的跌幅超越各國，前年僅3.3萬名難民獲入境安置，創10年新低。非法移民從2007年的1,220萬人，跌至2016年的1,070萬人，是2004年後最低。有51%美國人認同收容難民，而調查發現6至21歲的「後千禧年世代」，有望成為最具種族多元化思維的一代。<br />\n<br />\n中央社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n百年一遇　昆士蘭水災圍困數千人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n默克爾關閉fb官方賬戶"},{"pid":"4bf58f66492508cab9fea578c522f1d390319f83","tid":1006353,"uid":149306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"點會唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲資安危機鑊鑊新鮮鑊鑊金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94495ef016a35e09c50f055637c101b1437794e","tid":1006353,"uid":86628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"點解好似一堆唔同既新聞炒埋一獲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fa5d02ab0a1d61808808d42fbb9b0857bc7109","tid":1006353,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf58f66492508cab9fea578c522f1d390319f83","tid":1006353,"uid":149306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"點會唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲資安危機鑊鑊新鮮鑊鑊金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66cb0b00c3f9b69e37043218be6bd1877b81c2d","tid":1006353,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94495ef016a35e09c50f055637c101b1437794e","tid":1006353,"uid":86628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"點解好似一堆唔同既新聞炒埋一獲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"做個cross-sectional 既survey啫 睇下當代人點睇而加"}]}